trans-unit.source: Provides a hash table / dictionary implementation that contains [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] resources used by components and other elements of a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] application.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en hash-tabell / ordliste implementering som inneholder [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] ressursene som brukes av komponenter og andre elementer i en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] programmet.

trans-unit.source: The items in a ResourceDictionary are not immediately processed when application code is loaded by a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] loader.
trans-unit.target: Elementene i en ResourceDictionary behandles ikke umiddelbart når programmet kode er lastet inn av en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] laster.

trans-unit.source: Instead, the ResourceDictionary persists as an object, and the individual values are processed only when they are specifically requested.
trans-unit.target: I stedet ResourceDictionary vedvarer som et objekt, og de individuelle verdiene behandles når de spesifikt er angitt.

trans-unit.source: The ResourceDictionary class is not derived from <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryBase>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ResourceDictionary er ikke utledet fra <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryBase>.</xref:System.Collections.DictionaryBase>

trans-unit.source: Instead, the ResourceDictionary class implements <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> but relies on a <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> internally.
trans-unit.target: I stedet ResourceDictionary klassen implementerer <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>, men avhengig av en <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>internt.</xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> </xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)], the ResourceDictionary class is typically an implicit collection element that is the object element value of several `Resources` properties, when given in property element syntax.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)], ResourceDictionary klassen er vanligvis en implisitt samlingselement som objektet elementverdien av flere `Resources` egenskaper, når angitt i egenskapen element syntaks.

trans-unit.source: For details on implicit collections in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], see [XAML Syntax In Detail](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For informasjon om implisitt samlinger i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], se [XAML syntaks i detalj](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: An exception is when you want to specify a merged dictionary; for details, see [Merged Resource Dictionaries](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Et unntak er når du vil angi en sammenslått ordliste; Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [sammen ressursen ordlister](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Another possible [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] usage is to declare a resource dictionary as a discrete [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] file, and either load it at run time with <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XamlReader.Load%2A> or include it in a (full-trust) project as a resource or loose file.
trans-unit.target: En annen mulig [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] er deklarere en ordliste for ressursen som en separat [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] fil, og enten lastes inn på kjøretidspunktet med <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XamlReader.Load%2A>eller inkludere det i et prosjekt (fullstendig klarering) som en ressurs eller miste filen.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XamlReader.Load%2A>

trans-unit.source: In this case, ResourceDictionary can be declared as an object element, serving as the root element of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet ResourceDictionary kan angis som en objekt-element, som betjener som rotelementet for den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: You must map the appropriate XML namespace values (default for the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] namespace and typically `x:` for the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] namespace) onto the ResourceDictionary element if you plan to use it as the root element.
trans-unit.target: Du må tilordne de riktige verdiene for XML-navneområdet (standard for den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] navneområde og vanligvis `x:` for den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] navneområdet) på elementet ResourceDictionary Hvis du planlegger å bruke den som rotelementet.

trans-unit.source: Then you can add child elements that define the resources, each with an value.
trans-unit.target: Deretter kan du legge til underordnede elementer som definerer ressurser, hver med en verdi.

trans-unit.target: ## XAML implisitt samlingen Bruk ``` ``` ## XAML verdier *resourcesProperty* en egenskap som angir en egenskapselement der verditypen for denne egenskapen er ResourceDictionary.

trans-unit.source: If you need to clear merged dictionary items, obtain the particular dictionary from <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.MergedDictionaries%2A> collection and specifically call Clear on that <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>, although typically the dictionaries are remote and you might not have access.

trans-unit.target: Da blir bare den grunnleggende ordlisten.

trans-unit.target: Avslutter initialiseringsfase og ugyldiggjøres tidligere treet slik at alle endringer til nøkler fasen av initialisering kan tas med i betraktningen.

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.BeginInit%2A>og EndInit følger en transaksjonsmodell.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.BeginInit%2A>

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.BeginInit%2A>merker ordlisten ikke startet og EndInit for den initialisert.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.BeginInit%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value associated with the given key.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir verdien som er forbundet med den angitte nøkkelen.

trans-unit.source: If the requested key is not in this resource dictionary, the framework resource system will also check the merged dictionaries.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den forespurte nøkkelen ikke er i denne ressursen ordlisten, sjekker også framework ressursen systemet sammenslåtte ordlister.

trans-unit.source: Checking a <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary> by item or index is not generally the preferred way to retrieve resources.
trans-unit.target: Kontroll av en <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>av elementet eller indeks er ikke vanligvis den foretrukne måten å hente ressurser.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: You should instead call methods that are capable of participating in the full resource lookup process and look up resources by their keys, and that can find the resources in applications or themes.
trans-unit.target: Du må i stedet kalle metoder som er klare til å delta i fullstendig ressursen oppslag prosessen og slå opp ressurser ved nøklene, og som kan finne ressursene i programmer eller oppsett.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.FindResource%2A> is such a method, and is present on any <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.FindResource%2A>er en slik metode, og finnes på en hvilken som helst <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement>.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement></xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.FindResource%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise your attempt to find the resource does not match the true run-time behavior.
trans-unit.target: Forsøket på å finne ressursen svarer ellers ikke true kjøretid virkemåten.

trans-unit.source: However, obtaining resources directly from an individual dictionary might be appropriate if you are retrieving resources from a known <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary> location, and are doing so to avoid the possible performance and scope implications of run-time key lookup.
trans-unit.target: Henting av ressurser direkte fra en ordliste for individuelle kan imidlertid være nødvendig hvis du skal hente ressurser fra en kjent <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>plassering, og gjøre så å unngå mulig ytelse og omfanget konsekvensene av kjøretid nøkkeloppslag.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: You do not use indexers to define collection members in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Du ikke bruker Indekserere til å definere medlemmer i samling i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Instead, you create child elements in markup.
trans-unit.target: I stedet må opprette du underordnede elementer i markup.

trans-unit.source: The child elements are either child elements of <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>, or of a property element where the property type is `ResourceDictionary`.
trans-unit.target: De underordnede elementene er enten underordnede elementer av <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>, eller av en egenskapselement der egenskapstypen er `ResourceDictionary`.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: For details, see the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] usage sections in <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] Bruk inndelinger i <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: A merged <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary> does not have resource elements defined within it in markup.
trans-unit.target: En sammenslått <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>har ikke ressursen elementer som er definert i den i markup.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Instead, the merged dictionary is a <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary> with no markup child elements defined (or with no elements added through code), but with a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] specified for <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.Source%2A>.
trans-unit.target: I stedet den sammenslåtte ordlisten er en <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>med ingen underordnede markeringselementer angitt (eller med ingen elementer som er lagt til med koden), men med en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] angitt for <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.Source%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.Source%2A> </xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.Source%2A> designation enables the merged dictionary to come from an external source, such as a separate resource assembly that ships with the application, "loose [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)]", or a specific localization or global resources assembly.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.Source%2A>angivelsen gjør det mulig for den sammenslåtte ordlisten kommer fra en ekstern kilde, for eksempel en egen ressurs-samling som følger med programmet, "miste [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)]", en bestemt lokalisering eller globale ressurser samlingen.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: Specifying resource elements within a <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary> that has <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.Source%2A> specified is not supported.
trans-unit.target: Angir ressursen elementer i en <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>som har <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.Source%2A>angitte støttes ikke.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.Source%2A> </xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Lookup behavior within the MergedDictionaries collection will search the last-added <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary> first, and the search stops as soon as a requested key is found.
trans-unit.target: Oppslags-virkemåte i samlingen MergedDictionaries søkes det siste lagt inn <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>først, og søk-stopper så snart forespurte nøkkelen finnes.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Duplicate keys across the collection of merged dictionaries are not illegal.
trans-unit.target: Identiske nøkler i samlingen av sammenslåtte ordlister er ugyldig.

trans-unit.source: For more information on merged dictionary behavior, see [Merged Resource Dictionaries](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om sammenslåtte ordliste virkemåte, kan du se [sammenslåtte ressursen ordlister](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] to load resources from.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] ikke laste inn ressurser fra.

trans-unit.source: Typically, Source is specified as a Pack URI, which references the location of a resource dictionary that is included as a noncompiled Resource or Content build action by your application building project.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis datakilde er angitt som en pakke-URI, som refererer til plasseringen for en ordliste for ressursen som er inkludert som en noncompiled ressurs eller innhold bygge handlingen av programmet bygge prosjektet.

trans-unit.source: For details on the Pack URI format, see [Pack URIs in WPF](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer informasjon om Pack URIen [Pack URIer i WPF](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Generally, the Source property is set only for a <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary> that is specified for the <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.MergedDictionaries%2A> property (either as a property element in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], or as a <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary> item of the collection in code).
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis egenskapen Source er angitt bare for en <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>som er angitt for den <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.MergedDictionaries%2A>egenskapen (enten som en egenskapselement i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], eller som en <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>element i samlingen i koden).</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary> </xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary.MergedDictionaries%2A> </xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: In this context, setting the value for Source will merge the dictionary contents found at the supplied [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] into the current <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: I denne konteksten angivelse av verdien for datakilden vil slå sammen ordliste innholdet på den angitte [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] til gjeldende <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>.</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.target: Last inn feil fører til at det oppstod et unntak.
